blithely run roughshod
for at least four weeks.

07:27.531 --> 07:29.738
My theory is that
you're running
a battery of tests

07:29.867 --> 07:31.573
to convince him that
you've saved his life,

07:31.702 --> 07:33.658
and then con him
into funding you to
hire back your team.

07:33.746 --> 07:35.236
What?
Your old team?

07:36.081 --> 07:38.037
What?
This is your new reality.

07:38.167 --> 07:40.328
You've got your office,
you've got neighbors,

07:40.419 --> 07:42.080
you've got one employee,
one volunteer

07:42.212 --> 07:45.045
until she finds
actual paid work
or gets sick of you.

07:45.174 --> 07:48.041
I talked to Chase and Taub.
They're willing to come back.

07:49.011 --> 07:50.421
What about Thirteen?

07:50.554 --> 07:55.048
Not a good choice.
She's not a long-term,
because she has no long-term.

07:55.934 --> 07:57.060
Not taking your calls?

07:58.729 --> 07:59.844
She will.

07:59.938 --> 08:01.439
Discharge the patient.

08:01.565 --> 08:04.932
Unexplained loss
of consciousness
could be cardiomyopathy,

08:05.069 --> 08:07.105
global anoxia,
subarachnoid hemorrhage...

08:07.237 --> 08:09.899
Dehydration.
He was given fluids,
and he got better.

08:10.032 --> 08:11.363
And I'm sure your tests
have come up negative,

08:11.450 --> 08:13.315
or you'd have
shut me up already.

08:13.410 --> 08:14.570
Which means he goes home.

08:17.247 --> 08:19.238
CHI: There is a symptom.

08:19.875 --> 08:21.411
Extreme altruism.

08:25.798 --> 08:27.629
You've got
two choices, House.

08:27.758 --> 08:29.840
You can recognize
that your patient is just

08:29.927 --> 08:32.043
a very nice, healthy guy
and send him home.

08:32.137 --> 08:34.719
Or you can consider
altruism a symptom,

08:34.807 --> 08:37.389
in which case,
you cannot take his money.

08:42.398 --> 08:44.559
Send him home.

08:44.650 --> 08:47.608
And check with admitting
for the net worth
of all new patients.

08:54.076 --> 08:55.782
(WOMAN TALKING ON PA)

08:59.957 --> 09:02.118
THIRTEEN: I'm not
coming back, House.

09:05.170 --> 09:07.456
Technically,
you're back right now.

09:09.341 --> 09:11.923
I need you to
stop calling me.

09:12.010 --> 09:13.875
The first 17 messages
were cute, but...

09:13.971 --> 09:16.212
I'm putting
the band back together.

09:16.306 --> 09:18.467
