you've never showed up
at my place,

09:18.559 --> 09:20.140
what with your
love of annoying me

09:20.227 --> 09:23.060
and your inability to
take no for an answer.

09:23.147 --> 09:24.557
I'm guessing ankle monitor.

09:28.819 --> 09:32.311
Guilty as charged.
Literally.

09:33.949 --> 09:35.485
I'm not a doctor
any more, House.

09:36.618 --> 09:39.610
The job went away
but not the profession.

09:40.330 --> 09:42.742
You look healthy,
so that's not it.

09:45.169 --> 09:47.410
You met a boy or a girl,

09:48.464 --> 09:50.329
fallen in love,
wanna be happy.

09:50.924 --> 09:54.462
