10:03.520 --> 10:04.600
(YAWNING)

10:05.355 --> 10:06.856
Turns out I like boring.

10:06.982 --> 10:09.018
No, you want to
like boring.

10:09.151 --> 10:10.357
But if you
actually liked boring,

10:10.444 --> 10:12.935
