10:21.705 --> 10:24.538
You showed up to tell me
that you don't
want to hear from me.

10:24.625 --> 10:26.957
That's a mixed signal.

10:27.044 --> 10:30.286
And I'm gonna choose to
listen to your actions
rather than your words,

10:30.380 --> 10:31.665
'cause they're more honest.

10:38.722 --> 10:40.132
BENJAMIN:
I'm a little confused.

10:40.224 --> 10:42.465
The test is
designed to determine
if your nerves are...

10:42.559 --> 10:45.551
